{
  "stem": "21437.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think that that was one of the reasons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think about everything else, he could have coped with it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was an adult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I think that he felt that it's not fair to his younger children for them to be in this situation.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then you didn't think if you become stronger because of this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Although I feel that in the long run, I've got certain resilience.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At times, have more resilience than other people who grew up in towns that were predominantly Jewish, when they had this-- when they were cushioned from all of this, you see?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where they sort of, you know-- wherever they went, the non-Jews were there who looked after, who did the physical work, who did the cleaning, who did looking to after the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], you know.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there was a lot of poverty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In a town like this where it was predominantly Jewish, it was a lot and lot of poverty.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was a time where the Jewish children, where they could not afford to go to high school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or if you-- I don't know one in how many thousands attended university, you did not sit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to stand in the back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I mean, I felt it even before I started school, but not to that extent than when I started school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was always.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, in this particular town-- I can only speak about this particular town in Upper Silesia, close to the German border.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know exactly before Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because for as long as I can remember, Hitler was in power.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I can't really-- there are not enough words to describe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It becomes a part of you, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
